      "content": "No, the second i do anything its alerted and countering. None of this go bullshit winds me up, you flail wildly random try this try that, you dont confirm anything, we got 387 potential services that are gonna interfere . Literally the second i do anything like that, especially running ubiquity, itll go karenzilla ",
